OL,3,CNew strength labels for topical
OL,4,Csteroids following 'extreme' reactions
OL,6,FSteroid creams used to treat skin
OL,7,Fconditions like eczema and psoriasis
OL,8,Fwill now carry new strength warnings
OL,9,Fin a world first.
OL,11,FThe Medicines and Healthcare
OL,12,FRegulatory Agency (MHRA), who regulate
OL,13,Fthe medicines we use in the UK, has
OL,14,Fannounced the labels will be rolled
OL,15,Fout over the next year.
OL,17,FThe move will simplify advice and sees
OL,18,Fsteroid products branded either
OL,19,F'mild', 'moderate', 'strong' or 'very
OL,20,Fstrong', depending on what's in them.
