OL,3,CNew strength labels for topical
OL,4,Csteroids following 'extreme' reactions
OL,6,FThe MHRA said they'd received almost
OL,7,F300 reports, via their Yellow Card
OL,8,Fscheme, of those having suffered
OL,9,Fadverse reactions to steroid products
OL,10,Fin the past two years.
OL,12,FProducts are often applied through
OL,13,Fsprays and creams, but some have
OL,14,Freported serious side effect including
OL,15,Fburning skin, open, oozing pores and
OL,16,Fextreme itching after their body
OL,17,F'withdraws' from the drugs.
