OL,3,CNew strength labels for topical
OL,4,Csteroids following 'extreme' reactions
OL,6,FSufferers previously told ITV News
OL,7,FTopical Steroid Withdrawal (TSW) has
OL,8,Fruined their lives, forced them into
OL,9,Fhospital and left them feeling
OL,10,Fsuicidal, and have accused GPs of
OL,11,F"gaslighting" them.
OL,13,FWhat is topical steroid withdrawal and
OL,14,Fwhy can its effects be so severe?
OL,16,FTopical steroids, also know as
OL,17,Fcorticosteroids, can be in the form of
OL,18,Fgels, creams and aerosol sprays and
OL,19,Fcan vary in strength.
