OL,6,FTheir regular use sees the body become
OL,7,Fmore dependent on them and can lead to
OL,8,Fsevere consequences as withdrawal
OL,9,Ftakes place.
OL,11,FMore than eight million UK children
OL,12,Fand adults thought to suffer from
OL,13,Fatopic eczema alone.
OL,15,FIt's been almost a year since ITV News
OL,16,Fspoke to Jack Taylor from Bolton.
