OL,4,Csteroids following 'extreme' reactions
OL,6,FReacting to the news that strength
OL,7,Flabelling would be rolled, Jack told
OL,8,Fus he was "deflated" and that
OL,9,Flabelling the potency of various
OL,10,Fproducts "was the first step in an
OL,11,Fextremely long way to go."
OL,13,FThe National Eczema Society have long
OL,14,Fcampaigned for the change. They said
OL,15,Fthey were 'proud that the new change
OL,16,Fhad been brought in.
