OL,6,FThe MHRA previously reviewed evidence
OL,7,Fon topical steroids back in 2019 which
OL,8,Fresulted in added information being
OL,9,Fincluded around some of the risks to
OL,10,Fpatient information leaflets.
OL,12,FAsked to respond at the time to the
OL,13,Fclaims of sufferers by ITV News, the
OL,14,FMHRA said: "When used correctly,
OL,15,Ftopical steroids are safe and highly
OL,16,Feffective treatments for skin
OL,17,Fconditions such as eczema, psoriasis,
OL,18,Fand atopic dermatitis.
