OL,6,F"To ensure that patients can use these
OL,7,Fproducts safely and effectively, we
OL,8,Fcontinue to review the safety of
OL,9,Ftopical steroids and options to
OL,10,Fminimise risks, including measures to
OL,11,Fimprove understanding of the safe use
OL,12,Fof these products."
OL,14,FThe MHRA have since insisted that
OL,15,Finstances of Topical Steroid
OL,16,FWithdrawal or TSW are still "rare".
